      "required": false,
      "helpText": "  A selection list may be displayed in an area several columns wide. The starting position and height of each column may be specified. However, it is not necessary because defaults values will be used. The defaults used assume that nothing else is going in the block except the selection list and that the entire block should be filled. ",
